AJAX
Asynchronous javascript and xml

html
javascript
xml
__

AJAX calls can send data to a server using GET or POST (eg)
and the catch the data sent by tgher server in response


AJAX calls cab ve nade via the XMLHttpRequest js object

eg,

var foo = new XMLHttpRequest();

foo.open("GET","info.txt",true);
foo.send();



IMPORT JQUERY SCRIPT


$.ajax( <SETTINGS> );

SETTINGS: associative array containing all info required to make given ajax call

keys:

url
type: method (get/post)
data: data to be sent
done: function to be called if server responds


$.ajax( {
  url: '\foo';
  type: 'GET';
  data: 'information';
  done: function (d) {console.log(d); }
}
);





